RESEARCH ALERT - Sumitomo Sitix raised . Yamaichi Research Institute of Securities and Economics Inc said it upgraded Sumitomo Sitix Corp to a " 1 " from its previous " 2 " . In its three - grade rating system , the research institute assigns a " 1 " rating to issues whose values it expects will outperform the Tokyo Stock Exchange first - section TOPIX index by more than 10 percentage points over the following six months . 
